Book.java - Contains "Book" class
Patron.java - Contains "Patron" class
Library.java - Contains "Library" class


=============================
=          Design           =
=============================
Most of my code design depends on the given API.
I decided that the book / patron ID will be his index on his books / patrons array.
Because of that I didn't need to save an index property and each one of the books and patrons
got his own uniq ID



